        "a34f6081-2778-463c-8074-6403bf19be80": {
          "type": "accordion_content",
          "settings": {
            "section_class": "section_class",
            "page": "",
            "title": "Shipping, Returns & Warranty",
            "text": "<p>SHIPPING</p><p>Worldwide<strong> </strong>shipping from Bali & Australia. Free EXPRESS Shipping for orders $250+ AUD.</p><p>International Express Shipping will be sent via DHL and will arrive in 2 - 4 days once dispatched.</p><p>Domestic Indonesian & Australian orders will be sent express and arrive in 1 - 3 days.</p><p>Please read more of our Shipping Policy <a href=\"/policies/shipping-policy\" title=\"Shipping Policy\">here.</a></p><p>RETURNS/EXCHANGES</p><p>Wetsuits purchased on sale, can be exchanged for another size only - no refunds on sale items.</p><p>See our returns policy <a href=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\" title=\"https://oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\">here.</a></p><p>Please follow instructions on our  <a href=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\" title=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/policies/refund-policy\">Returns </a>page.</p><p>WARRANTY</p><p>We stand by the quality of our swimsuits, they are tailor made with high quality Italian fabric. </p><p>We offer a 12 month warranty from date of purchase, shall the make, material or hardware malfunction.</p><p>Read more about our warranty <a href=\"/pages/warranty\" title=\"Warranty\">here.</a></p>",
            "default_open_accordion": false
          }
        },
        "0f909705-4368-4514-8d5e-71a0ac76a5cb": {
          "type": "accordion_content",
          "settings": {
            "section_class": "section_class",
            "page": "",
            "title": "Contact Us",
            "text": "<p>Have a question? You can reach us below or on live chat.</p><p><a href=\"mailto:customercare@oceansoulbali.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mailto:customercare@oceansoulbali.com\">Email</a></p><p><a href=\"http://wa.me/61407215854\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://wa.me/61407215854\">Whats App</a></p><p></p>",
            "default_open_accordion": false
          }
        },
        "da5688b2-ac81-441f-ad20-d8c5bf5c3484": {
          "type": "accordion_content",
          "settings": {
            "section_class": "section_class",
            "page": "",
            "title": "Product Care",
            "text": "<p><strong>Care Tips for Your Limestone Eco-prene Spring Suit</strong></p><p><strong>Rinse After Every Use</strong></p><p>After enjoying the water, rinse your suit thoroughly with fresh water to remove salt, sand, or chlorine. </p><p><strong>Dry It Flat and in the Shade</strong></p><p>Avoid hanging your suit in direct sunlight for extended periods. Lay it flat in a shaded, well-ventilated area to dry. Avoid twisting or wringing out the suit, as this can cause unnecessary strain on the fabric.</p><p><strong>Fold Gently—Don’t Worry About Creases</strong></p><p>Limestone Eco-prene is naturally durable and resilient. If you notice any creases or folds, don’t worry—they will smooth out over time as the material stretches during wear. For long-term storage, fold the suit loosely or roll it to prevent deep creases. But rest assured, creases won’t affect performance or comfort!</p>",
            "default_open_accordion": false
          }
        }
      },
