    "accordion_K3YKGe": {
      "type": "accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_pane_m6HGAA": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>We line all our snow white surf suits with a beige econyl sustainable fabric, to prevent them from becoming transparent.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_zwBQPA": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is the Sulawesi a good spring suit for colder waters?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, the <strong>Sulawesi spring suit</strong> features 2.5mm thick Eco-prene neoprene, which provides excellent insulation while maintaining flexibility.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_KNt9CH": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are these spring suits only for surfing and diving?",
            "content": "<p>Our spring suits are designed for all water lovers!  Some of our customers buy them just for snorkelling or swimming when the water is cold.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_Py7J3k": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I care for my wetsuit?",
            "content": "<p>Make sure after each wear you wash it with fresh water to remove salt and sand.  Then hang or lie flat in a shady area.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_99R9Rk": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I return it if it's not the right size or if I don't like it?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely!  Process all returns via our website portal <a href=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/a/returns\" title=\"https://www.oceansoulbali.com/a/returns\">here.</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_cYX4Eg": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How should I store my spring suit?",
            "content": "<p>Fold your suit in half and hang it over a padded coat hanger.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_ArMU9p": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do limestone wetsuits crease more than rubber ones?",
            "content": "<p>Being a memory foam, creasing is a normal part of the material properties. Wearing the wetsuit and letting it mould to your body will reduce the creases over time. Soaking in warm water can also help to relax the creases.</p><p></p>"
          }
        }
      },
